OASISFormat: 0.4
Name: ocsipersist
Version: 3.4.0
Homepage: http://ocsigen.org/tyxml/
Authors:
  Vincent Balat,
  Gabriel Kerneis,
  Gabriel Radanne

Synopsis: Simple k/v store interface to be used by an ocsigen server.

License: LGPL-2.1 with OCaml linking exception
Plugins: META (0.3), DevFiles (0.3)
BuildTools: ocamlbuild

AlphaFeatures: pure_interface


Flag dbm
  Description: Build the dbm module.
  Default: false

Flag sqlite
  Description: Build the sqlite module.
  Default: false

Flag pgsql
  Description: Build the pgsql module.
  Default: false

Flag webstorage
  Description: Build the Web Storage module.
  Default: false

Executable "ocsidbm"
  Path: src_dbm
  Build$: flag(dbm)
  MainIs: ocsidbm.ml
  CompiledObject: best
  BuildDepends: lwt.unix, dbm

Library ocsipersist
  Path: src
  Modules: Ocsipersist_sig, Ocsipersist
  BuildDepends: lwt

